5:["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L17",null,{"value":[{"value":"예시","id":"예시","depth":2},{"value":"Props","id":"props","depth":2},{"value":"코드","id":"코드","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L18",null,{}],["$","$L19",null,{"metadata":"$2:props:children:props:children:2:props:pageMap:4:children:4:frontMatter","bottomContent":"$undefined","sourceCode":"# Checkbox\n\n선택 입력용 체크박스 컴포넌트입니다. Base UI의 headless Checkbox를 기반으로 합니다.\n\n## 예시\n\n<ComponentPreview>\n  <CheckboxDemo />\n</ComponentPreview>\n\n## Props\n\n`Checkbox`는 Base UI Checkbox의 props와 호환되며, `label`을 주면 레이블이 함께 렌더링됩니다. `disabled`, `checked`, `defaultChecked` 등 표준 체크박스 속성을 지원합니다.\n\n## 코드\n\n```tsx\nimport { Checkbox } from \"pine-design-system\";\n\n<Checkbox label=\"Accept terms\" defaultChecked />\n```","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"id":"$undefined","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Checkbox","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":"선택 입력용 체크박스 컴포넌트입니다. Base UI의 headless Checkbox를 기반으로 합니다."}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"예시","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["예시",["$","$L1a",null,{"id":"예시"}]]}],"\n",["$","$L1b",null,{"children":["$","$L1c",null,{}]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"props","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["Props",["$","$L1a",null,{"id":"props"}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":[["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"Checkbox"}],"는 Base UI Checkbox의 props와 호환되며, ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"label"}],"을 주면 레이블이 함께 렌더링됩니다. ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"disabled"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"checked"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"defaultChecked"}]," 등 표준 체크박스 속성을 지원합니다."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"코드","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["코드",["$","$L1a",null,{"id":"코드"}]]}],"\n",["$","div",null,{"data-pagefind-ignore":"all","className":"nextra-code x:relative x:not-first:mt-[1.25em]","children":["$undefined",["$","pre",null,{"className":"x:group x:focus-visible:nextra-focus x:overflow-x-auto x:subpixel-antialiased x:text-[.9em] x:bg-white x:dark:bg-black x:py-4 x:ring-1 x:ring-inset x:ring-gray-300 x:dark:ring-neutral-700 x:contrast-more:ring-gray-900 x:contrast-more:dark:ring-gray-50 x:contrast-more:contrast-150 x:rounded-md not-prose","tabIndex":"0","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"x:group-hover:opacity-100 x:group-focus:opacity-100 x:opacity-0 x:transition x:focus-within:opacity-100 x:flex x:gap-1 x:absolute x:right-4 x:top-2","children":[["$","$L1d",null,{"children":["$","svg",null,{"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"currentColor","height":"1em","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M4 19h6v-2H4v2zM20 5H4v2h16V5zm-3 6H4v2h13.25c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2s-.9 2-2 2H15v-2l-3 3l3 3v-2h2c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4z"}]}]}],false]}],["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#D73A49","--shiki-dark":"#F97583"},"children":"import"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#24292E","--shiki-dark":"#E1E4E8"},"children":" { Checkbox } "}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#D73A49","--shiki-dark